  <trk>
    <name>ATH-L2 — Meteora &amp; Thessaly Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from ATH and ride into the Meteora &amp; Thessaly. Hit Lamia and Meteora Rock Pillars — 400m. Loop back to ATH over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
